data.title: 以至少 50 个字回答问题
data.content: "Describe a time you learned how to do something new. What did you learn? How did you learn it?"
data.answer: In my most recent role, I was unfamiliar with my company's record-keeping system at first. After a few days of the job training, I was able to maintain the record-keeping system, but I still wasn't happy with my fluency. I found tutorials online and spent evenings training myself to a deeper level of knowledge. I became fluent in the program in no time flat. It was nice to dive in, learn the system well, and have that sense of accomplishment early on in my role. （85 字）
